## 10. Existing App/Blueprint to Clone for Scaffold

The demo is a new static 4-page site with no dependencies on existing portfolio apps. No clone needed. Start from scratch with the file structure in `planner.out`:
```
index.html | services.html | projects.html | contact.html
style.css | main.js | projects.js | contact.js
```

The `AppFrame.jsx` component in the portfolio site (`src/components/AppFrame.jsx`) handles the iframe shell for the `/work-samples/construction-company-website` route — no changes needed there.

For `workSamples.js` — check the current last `id` with:
```bash
grep '"id":' ../michaelwegter.com/src/data/workSamples.js | tail -1
```
Then use `next_id = last_id + 1`.
